Package: MitoDiveR
Type: Package
Title: Comparative Mitochondrial Genomics in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael W.", "Sandel", 
           email = "michael.sandel@msstate.edu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for comparative analysis, annotation parsing, and 
    visualization of mitochondrial genomes across species. MitoDiveR 
    enables import of annotated mitogenomes, extraction of gene features, 
    comparison of gene content and order, analysis of sequence divergence, 
    and preparation of datasets for evolutionary and phylogenetic studies.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
